      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i get the theory but it just sounds so weird. like, if there isn't any signal or hidden code, it's almost like something is actively interfering or hiding the truth from us. is there any concept in physics that deals with things being \"hidden\" or things acting in ways that seem almost malicious to our observations?",
